#: ../../source/currency.rst:35
msgid ""
"In templates, instead of using the ``c()`` function, you should use the ``|"
"c`` filter. For example, ``{{ 20|c }}`` displays as ``20 points``."
msgstr ""
"在模板中，你应当使用 ``|c`` 过滤器而不是 ``c()`` 函数。举例来说， ``{{ 20|"
"c }}`` 会显示为 ``20 points``."

#: ../../source/currency.rst:42
msgid "payoffs"
msgstr "收益"

#: ../../source/currency.rst:44
msgid ""
"Each player has a ``payoff`` field. If your player makes money, you should "
"store it in this field. ``self.participant.payoff`` automatically stores the "
"sum of payoffs from all subsessions. You can modify ``self.participant."
"payoff`` directly, e.g. to round the final payoff to a whole number."
msgstr ""
"每位玩家都有一个 ``payoff`` 字段。如果你的玩家获得了钱，你应当将其存在此字段"
"中。 ``self.participant.payoff`` 自动存储了所有子会话的收益之和。你可以直接修"
"改 ``self.participant.payoff`` ，例如将最终收益四舍五入变为整数。"

#: ../../source/currency.rst:50
msgid ""
"At the end of the experiment, a participant's total profit can be accessed "
"by ``self.participant.payoff_plus_participation_fee()``; it is calculated by "
"converting ``self.participant.payoff`` to real-world currency (if "
"``USE_POINTS`` is ``True``), and then adding ``self.session."
"config['participation_fee']``."
msgstr ""
"在实验结束时，参与人的总收益可以通过 ``self.participant."
"payoff_plus_participation_fee()`` 获取；这是通过将 ``self.participant."
"payoff`` 转换为真实世界的货币（如果 ``USE_POINTS`` 为 ``True``），再加上 "
"``self.session.config['participation_fee']`` 计算得来的。"

#: ../../source/currency.rst:59
msgid "Points (i.e. \"experimental currency\")"
msgstr "点数（即“实验货币”）"

#: ../../source/currency.rst:61
msgid ""
"If you set ``USE_POINTS = True``, then currency amounts will be points "
"instead of dollars/euros/etc. For example, ``c(10)`` is displayed as ``10 "
"points`` (or ``10 puntos``, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"你可以设置 ``USE_POINTS = True``，那么货币值就会使用点数而不是美元/欧元/等"
"等。举例来说， ``c(10)`` 会被显示为 ``10 points`` （或者 ``10 puntos``, 诸如"
"此类）"

#: ../../source/currency.rst:64
msgid ""
"You can decide the conversion rate to real money by adding a "
"``real_world_currency_per_point`` entry to your session config."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过在你的session config中增加一个 ``real_world_currency_per_point`` 条"
"目来决定到实际货币的转化率。"

